                li I was lucky enough to be chosen to represent Skate 3 at our London EA Showcase Event
                    ul.nested
                        li.nested This event featured a number of EA published games, and was a great chance to socialize with marketing
                        li.nested The event was two grueling days, 9-9 each day, with after events
